type: web_research
title: MCP Marketing Automation & LINE Integration Research 2025-2026
key_insights[13]: 313+ MCP servers available for marketing automation on mcpmarket.com,ActiveCampaign is the only MCP server that can add/remove contacts from live automations,HubSpot released official MCP server (public beta) with read-only CRM access and OAuth 2.0,"Salesforce MCP is in Pilot status via Agentforce, pricing TBD","LINE officially released line-bot-mcp-server on GitHub with 11 tools (push/broadcast messages, rich menu, profiles)",Lステップ launched Webhook転送 (July 2025) and API連携 features enabling bidirectional integration with AI,エルメ supports Webhook + Messaging API for external AI integration but no direct MCP server,プロライン has no MCP or advanced API integration found,No Japanese LINE marketing tools (Lステップ/エルメ/プロライン) have native MCP servers,Zapier exposes MCP endpoints for 30k+ actions,n8n supports MCP natively and has deep LangChain integration,Claude Hub enables autonomous GitHub bot via webhooks,Claude Code hooks support MCP tool matching with regex patterns
findings[10]: "MCP ecosystem: 9,700万+ monthly SDK downloads, 10,000+ active servers as of 2025","Key marketing MCP servers: ActiveCampaign, HubSpot, Google Ads, Meta Ads, Amazon Ads, Coupler.io, GA4, Zapier, n8n, WordPress","LINE Bot MCP Server: 11 tools including push_text_message, push_flex_message, broadcast, get_profile, rich_menu management","Lステップ API連携: requires Pro plan+, uses Make/Zapier as middleware, can connect to OpenAI/Dify for AI chat","Lステップ Webhook転送: 月額5,500円 additional option, enables hub-style routing to multiple external tools","エルメ: Webhook-based external integration possible, no dedicated MCP server, uses Make/Zapier for AI connection",Claude Code headless mode (-p flag) enables script-based automation without interactive prompts,"Claude Hub: Docker-based GitHub webhook bot, spawns containers per request, autonomous for hours","Workflow automation market: $29.95B in 2025, projected $87.74B by 2032","n8n-MCP provides AI assistants access to 1,084 n8n workflow nodes"
recommendations[5]: Build custom MCP server wrapping Lステップ API for direct Claude integration,"Use LINE Bot MCP Server as foundation, extend with Lステップ webhook relay",Consider n8n as middleware between Claude and Japanese marketing tools,ActiveCampaign MCP is most feature-rich for marketing automation,"For Japanese market: LINE Bot MCP + Lステップ Webhook + Make/n8n is the most viable stack"
